OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FLise McNally reports from Westminster
OL,7,Fon a historic day for Hillsborough
OL,8,Fcampaigners.
OL,10,FAfter nearly four decades of fighting
OL,11,Ffor justice the Hillsborough families,
OL,12,Fsurvivors and campaigners have marked
OL,13,Fa major milestone as a law named in
OL,14,Fmemory of those who died was
OL,15,Funanimously backed by MPs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F97 Liverpool fans were unlawfully
OL,7,Fkilled and then lied about - with
OL,8,Fauthorities and some in the media
OL,9,Fblaming them for a fatal stadium crush
OL,10,Fin 1989 which saw a police force
OL,11,Frepeatedly cover up its mistakes.
OL,13,FThe Hillsborough Law aims to end that
OL,14,Fcover up culture, bringing in a legal
OL,15,Frequirement to tell the truth in
OL,16,Finvestigations or inquiries and giving
OL,17,Ffamilies the power they need to pursue
OL,18,Fa case in court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FSpeaking for the first time since he
OL,7,Fwas re-elected to parliament Andy
OL,8,FBurnham said the law would "rewire the
OL,9,Fstate and pass power to the hands of
OL,10,Fordinary people".
OL,12,FThe prime minister-in-waiting thanked
OL,13,Fhis "friend" Sir Keir Starmer for his
OL,14,Fwork on the draft law, paying tribute
OL,15,Fto his "commitment to a country based
OL,16,Fon justice and fairness".
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@LO]wD@HOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
