OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FThe legislation, which is formally
OL,7,Fcalled the Public Office
OL,8,F(Accountability) Bill, was passed
OL,9,Funanimously by MPs at third reading on
OL,10,F14 July.
OL,12,FIt will now be sent to the House of
OL,13,FLords for further scrutiny before it
OL,14,Fcan become law.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FAfter stalling, following concerns
OL,7,Ffrom campaigners over its application
OL,8,Fto intelligence agencies, it was
OL,9,Famended to bring spies within the
OL,10,Fscope of the duty of candour, but with
OL,11,Fa "secure process" for disclosing
OL,12,Finformation that could affect national
OL,13,Fsecurity.
OL,15,FMargaret Aspinall's 18-year-old son
OL,16,FJames died in the disaster.
OL,18,FFor the families who have campaigned
OL,19,Ftirelessly for justice, the law has
OL,20,Fbeen a long time coming.
OL,26,@sD@COUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
