OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FMargaret Aspinall's 18-year-old son
OL,7,FJames died in the disaster, and paying
OL,8,Ftribute to him she said it was because
OL,9,Fof him they had now done "the right
OL,10,Fthing for this country".
OL,12,F"I thank my son who died at
OL,13,FHillsborough," she said.
OL,15,F"He's introduced me through his death
OL,16,Fto so many wonderful people, but he
OL,17,Falso introduced me to the right people
OL,18,Fto do the right thing for this
OL,19,Fcountry, so thank you James.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F"He'd be very proud because he was a
OL,7,Fpeople's person so hopefully he's up
OL,8,Fthere cheering."
OL,10,F"It'll make a massive impact because
OL,11,Fif you look at Grenfell, contaminated
OL,12,Fblood, the Arena bombing, the Post
OL,13,FOffice scandal so many who are still
OL,14,Ftrying to get the truth, to get the
OL,15,Fjustice that they deserve," she added.
OL,17,F"Don't forget with Hillsborough we got
OL,18,Fno accountability. We got the truth
OL,19,Fbut we had no accountability so this
OL,20,Fwill have a massive impact to help
OL,21,Fthem."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FSue Roberts' brother Graham was killed
OL,7,Fin the disaster.
OL,9,FSue Roberts' brother Graham was 24
OL,10,Fwhen he died, she said: "We've had
OL,11,Fknock backs since 1989, but if
OL,12,Fsomething's important, you can't just
OL,13,Fwalk away.
OL,15,F"This isn't for us. This is for the
OL,16,Fgood of other people and what might
OL,17,Fhappen in the future. We don't want
OL,18,Fanyone to suffer the way we suffered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F"You know, we have to raise funds, to
OL,7,Fpay for our legal representation. We
OL,8,Fwere always outfunded, you know, the
OL,9,Flies that were told time and time
OL,10,Fagain.
OL,12,F"They were paid to tell their lies.
OL,13,FThe truth was hidden from us,
OL,14,Fdocuments were released to us that
OL,15,Fshould have been in the public domain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F"Now, right from the early days, when
OL,7,Fthe police officers were told not to
OL,8,Fwrite in, then they books, which's
OL,9,Fbeen one frustration after another,
OL,10,Fbut if we gave up, then the same thing
OL,11,Fcould happen again and again.
OL,13,F"You know, every documentary you see,
OL,14,Fthe post office, it was like, This is
OL,15,FHillsborough all over again. Nobody's
OL,16,Flearnt anything. This is why we need a
OL,17,FHillsborough, so that in future, it
OL,18,Fwon't happen. People will be treated
OL,19,Ffairly."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FCharlotte Hennessey was just six when
OL,7,Fher dad Jimmy was killed. "I was
OL,8,Fobviously too young back then," she
OL,9,Fsaid, "but Hillsborough family members
OL,10,Fhad to fundraise and use savings, to
OL,11,Fbe able to have legal representation.
OL,13,F"Families won't have to go through
OL,14,Fthat now.
OL,16,F"They'll be entitled to legal aid if
OL,17,Ftheir loved one was killed in a state
OL,18,Frelated death, and I think that's
OL,19,Fincredible, it takes so much pressure
OL,20,Foff if you're going through the worst
OL,21,Ftime of your life as it is."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,FLabour MP Ian Byrne, who was at
OL,7,FHillsborough, was visibly emotional as
OL,8,Fhe spoke during a debate on the law.
OL,10,FHolding back tears, the Liverpool West
OL,11,FDerby MP said: "To every survivor, I
OL,12,Fhope today brings some measure of
OL,13,Fpeace.
OL,15,F"Not because it can erase the past,
OL,16,Fnothing ever will, but because your
OL,17,Fsuffering has brought us about lasting
OL,18,Fchange for generations to come.
OL,26,@sD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F"For decades I asked myself why I
OL,7,Fsurvived. Today, I think, I
OL,8,Funderstand. Not because I've done
OL,9,Fanything extraordinary, but because I
OL,10,Fwas given the privilege of standing
OL,11,Fhere and carrying the voices of people
OL,12,Fwho could no longer speak for
OL,13,Fthemselves.
OL,15,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne
OL,16,Fspeaking during the Hillsborough Law
OL,17,Fdebate.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F"If in some small way I have honoured
OL,7,Fthe memory of the 97, if I've been
OL,8,Fworthy of the trust the families and
OL,9,Fsurvivors have placed in me, if this
OL,10,FParliament finally ensures that no
OL,11,Fgrieving family will ever have to come
OL,12,Fto fight the state simply to uncover
OL,13,Fthe truth, then every setback, every
OL,14,Fdisappointment, every sleepless night
OL,15,Fwould have been worth it.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784114301
OL,3,CMilestone for Hillsborough campaigners
OL,4,Cas law unanimously backed
OL,6,F"This law is far more than
OL,7,FHillsborough. It is about the kind of
OL,8,Fcountry we choose to be, a country
OL,9,Fwhere power tells the truth, where
OL,10,Fpublic servants serve the public,
OL,11,Fwhere justice is not delayed until
OL,12,Fcampaigners grow old, and where no
OL,13,Ffamily is ever left to walk alone."
OL,15,FIn a rare diversion from parliamentary
OL,16,Fprotocol, MPs applauded Mr Byrne's
OL,17,Fspeech in the Commons.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
